12000&v=beta&t=4ZgfB8_gOTqbxjJizGzWIgyV2nTVVoUjkoICmKnFpyM", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/public_identifier": "ashish-battoo-5533ba13", "peopleAlsoViewed/24/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAK6lY8BojG3Gf_r3GsTDAVseEJzlAh9US0", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/entity_urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAFehNGgB2U8qVNLlML3pS8qPYxuaP5DoLBY", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/first_name": "Parth", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/follower_count": "101", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/headline": "Student at University of Bath", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/last_name": "Hingorani", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/premium": "false", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/profile_picture": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D03AQH4Vv2S7V45zQ/profile-displayphoto-crop_800_800/B4DZnTOCNNKQAI-/0/1760185296416?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=2KjG_T1Ko1bu71Tz4T3x0XGKDsQATHgsO0Z8XmmLLsg", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/public_identifier": "parth-hingorani-088440350", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAFehNGgB2U8qVNLlML3pS8qPYxuaP5DoLBY", "profilePic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQEWqzdjy8JhzA/profile-displayphoto-crop_800_800/B56Zyoe_K8K4AI-/0/1772353224314?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=03sGJQSKazEDIa8OzHKmK14PrrSqBAdx4ci2Q5WwRH0", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQEWqzdjy8JhzA/profile-displayphoto-crop_800_800/B56Zyoe_K8K4AI-/0/1772353224314?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=03sGJQSKazEDIa8OzHKmK14PrrSqBAdx4ci2Q5WwRH0", "publicIdentifier": "aditya-shamsher-malla-05421a6", "recommendations/0/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Aji directly", "recommendations/0/date": "August 24, 2024", "recommendations/0/description": "- Aji, through his creativity, dedication and eagerness to learn, won the admiration of guests, respect from his colleagues/ team as well as laurels from TripAdvisor!\n- A thorough professional balancing the quest for quality, detail and the welfare of his team\n- He was instrumental, as part of a crack team, helping me reposition an iconic thirty years old property into a gleaming full service flagship of a new brand affiliated to The Ascott Ltd Indonesia\n- Highly recommended as a luxury Hotel Housekeeper or even a Rooms Division Leader, a challenge he rose up to willingly on several occasions!", "recommendations/0/name": "Aji Kusuma Putra", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Executive Housekeeper", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/aji-kusuma-putra-868909101/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABnw_ZABE1hWgqb0e9KOmlvpMx0vS6k3nRQ", "recommendations/1/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Sarthak directly", "recommendations/1/date": "February 26, 2023", "recommendations/1/description": "Sarthak was on my team during a transition phase at Shangri-La New Delhi. A short but critical period in the midst of restructuring  the sales team and customer segments. Broad shoulders, a responsible attitude and deep intelligence personified Sarthak. He provided impactful leadership developing and strengthening corporate business for the hotel as we leveraged the brand and broke away from low yielding volume businesses. His entrepreneurial skills shone even at that time. All the best Sarthak!", "recommendations/1/name": "Sarthak Khanna", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Co-Founder & Director at senOcare, India | Chief Executive Officer - MICE & More Services", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sarthakkhanna10/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAHPdnYB3H11SNhrRfuypAXffLxxFVbtYsI", "recommendations/2/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Chiranjibi directly", "recommendations/2/date": "February 26, 2023", "recommendations/2/description": "Chiranjibi was part of a team that had witnessed a crash of the business and property resulting in a distress sale. He quickly adapted to the new reality, embraced change, upskilled himself and in fact emerged as a leader transforming his team. Yes, all this as a Housekeeping Supervisor, forming the backbone of service delivery, process alignment, efficiencies and business results in a difficult market. I was fortunate to have such a focused team member on my team and attribute much of the success and turnaround achieved at Four Points by Sheraton Visakhapatnam to his contributions. A positive minded and diligent professional, he is an asset to any organisation looking for a leader in service delivery, and customer success.", "recommendations/2/name": "Chiranjibi Panda", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Experienced Hospitality Leader | Executive Housekeeper | Expert in Operations, Team Building & Guest Experience | Committed to Growth with Purpose", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/chiranjibi-panda/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABSnHigB39Q3vgqkzPz16esassAy-dQ636A", "recommendations/3/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Sagar directly", "recommendations/3/date": "February 26, 2023", "recommendations/3/description": "Sagar is one of the most diligent, intelligent and thoughtful professionals I have had the privilege of working with. A conscientious team player, his creative initiatives towards quality and consistency ensure efficiencies and enhanced customer satisfaction scores. The ideal co-pilot while negotiating turbulence, Sagar knows how to hold his nerve and follow the checklist, while initiating critical procedures to ensure order, safety of the asset, personnel and lives (yes, as a hotelier, your decisions often decide the fate of several lives entrusted to you).  On the business side, Sagar understands trends, is analytical and recommends and acts on course correction looking at market forces and revenue inputs. He asks the right questions while challenging and supporting his tram at the same time. Having demonstrated a keen learning mindset through his career, I think the time is apt for Sagar to take on an independent property leadership role and I am proud to recommend him for one.", "recommendations/3/name": "Sagar Gaonkar, CHA", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "General Manager at Marriott International", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sagar-gaonkar-cha-4538ab3a/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAhRtr8Bxz0yOCDW-dQOyETAetvdpNr-NOg", "recommendations/4/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Jayeesha directly", "recommendations/4/date": "May 12, 2022", "recommendations/4/description": "I had the privilege of working with Jayeesha as we negotiated a competitive environment to reposition the hotel by leveraging the brand and creating new opportunities.  Jayeesha was quick on the uptake, with sound knowledge of her subject. She led marketing initiatives aligning with the strategy, driving various stakeholders, including vendors to achieve desired results. Do not be misled by her quiet demeanor, for when it's about the brand, she means business! Assertive, with a creative mind and a learning mindset, she is a great asset to any hospitality business looking to make a mark. The hotel and I owe a lot to her in setting the direction towards sustained market leadership. Wishing her continued success.", "recommendations/4/name": "Jayeesha M.", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Head of Marketing Communications & PR | Luxury & Lifestyle Hospitality | Brand Strategy | Media Relations | Reputation Management", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jayeesha-m-65393a59/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAxrNh8BzB58jy0_evFA7LWhGnOtsUfcfKg", "recommendations/5/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Soumodeep directly", "recommendations/5/date": "July 5, 2021", "recommendations/5/description": "I had the privilege of having Soumo on my team during an extremely challenging assignment in 2012. The ask was a change of strategy and mindset. Soumo promptly rose to the occasion by getting his head around the objectives, aligning himself with the goal and also motivating his team members while maintaining his characteristic calm. A thinker you would want on your team particularly during a crisis, and he has faced many - always coming out on top of the situation. Over the years, he has demonstrated sound leadership skills and strong values. He has much left in him for the hospitality industry to gain from.", "recommendations/5/name": "Soumodeep Bhattacharya", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "A seasoned Sales and Marketing professional with over 19 years of experience in lifestyle and concept selling.", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/soumodeep-bhattacharya-32634a21/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAR__U4BqnnXA9ZeIs16ENLxstKO5ah-5yY", "recommendations/6/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with DR MALIHA H on the same team", "recommendations/6/date": "May 8, 2021", "recommendations/6/description": "With the onset of the pandemic last year, we were looking at ways to address the needs of our Team Members, stranded across the country while some held fort at the Hotel. The need for psychological intervention became apparent pretty soon as the reality dwelled upon us (or did it). Dr Maliha Sable, an energetic voice on the phone then, came as a much needed relief. We had her address our Team Members in batches, overcoming the constraints of physical distancing and connecting individually with everyone at the personal level via video conferencing. Her sessions proved to be very effective, for the homework she had done to understand the business, individual work profile as well as specific challenges was commendable. Dr Maliha managed to bring in a balance in the thought process of each Team Member, connecting them to reality and helping them own their circle of influence. We are grateful for her contribution and wish her success in her endeavours!", "recommendations/6/name": "DR MALIHA H SABLE", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Founder | ‘25 ’26 Global Business Leader by Private Office Of Royal Family UAE | Global Icon of the Year Recipient | Asia’s Most Promising Doctor & Influential Face Global | Globally Acclaimed Excellence in Mental Health", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/dr-maliha-h-sable-b74815179/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACpNKUgB3dv-F-rUXaTZRRAQ5Myqfc5em08", "recommendations/7/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Rakesh Kumar but on different teams", "recommendations/7/date": "February 24, 2021", "recommendations/7/description": "Rakesh has gained extensive knowledge and competence in his area of expertise. One of the few professionals with all round experience in setting up and operating laundry operations as well as pre-opening Capex and Opex for equipment and linen. Rakesh combines his amiable personality with sharp focus on deliverables to create a healthy and productive work environment demonstrating measurable results, consistently. Highly recommended for new projects and renovation/ restructuring/ consultancy assignments.", "recommendations/7/name": "Rakesh Kumar Dureja", "recommendations/7/subtitle": "Sound Product, Production knowledge about Garments Processing for Commercial ,Hotel & Hospital Laundries.Trainer for Young Brigade. Available for Visiting Consultant Roles 📞 +917838850444", "recommendations/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rakesh-kumar-dureja-a7679a14/", "recommendations/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAL2tnoBr19T9kPOB1Y0sPVPitbrZ5iWi5M", "recommendations/8/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Shree  directly", "recommendations/8/date": "January 6, 2021", "recommendations/8/description": "Impactful. That’s the first word among a few others that comes to my mind when I reflect upon the time that Shree chose to join my team at The Oberoi Grand- her first role after college. She also brought with her honesty, integrity, conviction, grit and commitment. So significant was her contribution that it remains for me one of the finest examples of sales execution and relationship building in a challenging (and somewhat hostile market). She did not let her lack of local language knowledge deter her, and no, she did not buy time to devise an outlandish strategy to overcome the handicap - she simply learnt the language in less than three months to be able to connect with her customers and build strong relationships on behalf of her Organisation. Shree believes in letting her work speak for itself and the organisation, which will certainly not miss the attention of peers and superiors. I maintain that I was indeed fortunate to have worked with (and learnt from) an astute professional like Shree. She has shown even greater skills in deftly managing various aspects of her journey in professional and personal spheres. What a pleasure it is to see her continue to make a mark in the corporate world.", "recommendations/8/name": "Shree  P Singh", "recommendations/8/subtitle": "Trusted Advisor to Enterprises| Consultative Sales and Client Success| CXO Engagement| Enterprise Growth Leader| Driving Revenues, Relationships and Retention", "recommendations/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/shree-prabha-singh/", "recommendations/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAArQ7oUBiRDam0CF6_XD1eZqP-FXmgKkKSU", "recommendations/9/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Sardar on the same team", "recommendations/9/date": "July 14, 2020", "recommendations/9/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Sardar at The Westin Mumbai Garden City. I found Sardar to be a very level headed, focused IT specialist who would understand the challenges in detail and respond with innovative solutions. Never to drag his heels, Sardar was one of the more proactive members in this hotel finding ways to add value to the guests’ and associates’ experience. A highly recommended resource for a pre opening or an operational hotel team.", "recommendations/9/name": "Sardar Pachimbare", "recommendations/9/subtitle": "Cluster IT Manager at The Ritz-Carlton Hotel Company, L.L.C.", "recommendations/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sarpachimbare/", "recommendations/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAf8490BBIcgpXyOoJlPWJiuOjy7hdGRX-E", "recommendations/10/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Yogabala directly", "recommendations/10/date": "July 11, 2020", "recommendations/10/description": "Yoga, as we fondly called her was the omnipresent saviour in critical situations. She often surprised us with her brilliant ideas AND execution. Quiet and thoughtful in her delivery, she is also confident enough to express her opinion and ensure she is heard. The best way to get her all charged up and motivated is to throw a tough challenge at her. Very resourceful and persistent, she would raise the bar each time. I wish her continued success and recognition in what she loves doing. ", "recommendations/10/name": "Yogabala Mahapatra", "recommendations/10/subtitle": "HR Business Partner | Scaling Tech & Ops Teams | HRBP, ER, Performance, Org Design", "recommendations/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yogabala-mahapatra-245602b8/", "recommendations/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABkBltUB9vPIjoPr2qCQN3GxUSmmmazmkKo", "recommendations/11/date": "July 3, 2020", "recommendations/11/description": "A humble, quiet worker, Rahul lets his work speak for him. I have seen him grow into leadership roles, transitioning from a strategic thinker at The Westin Hyderabad Mindspace to a thought leader at Hilton. He has demonstrated sharp analytical skills as well as persistence while chasing tough objectives. He is the right mix of attitude and knowledge and sure to deliver the results when you need the most.", "recommendations/11/name": "Rahul Tandon, CRME, CHBA, CHIA, CAHTA", "recommendations/11/subtitle": "Director of Revenue Management | Global Market Experience | AI-Driven Strategist | Turning Data Into Revenue", "recommendations/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rahultandonca/", "recommendations/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAfKe5EBRueTE_QOhYMv7OdytKehcPA-k4E", "recommendations/12/date": "July 3, 2020", "recommendations/12/description": "Ryena, already much awarded and recognised by the industry is indeed worth every word in her praise. She was thrown into the deep end during her first role back in India as part of my team at The Oberoi Grand. I was truly amazed at her ability to balance the need to deliver results and learn the complexities of the responsibility thrust upon her as part of a rejig. She stood out from her peers due to her sense of responsibility, ethics and loyalty. She won the confidence of customers, peers and seniors quickly, even when she was brought in to fill a sudden void in a new market at the mammoth 427 rooms Westin Hyderabad Mindspace. I was privileged to have her strengthen the Team as she turned out to be a significant contributor to the Hotel’s meteoric ramp up and rise to a market leader position. Never to shy away from a new challenge, Ryena is a true example of competence - as I often say - Skill, Will and Attitude. She continues to make me and all those who place their trust on her, proud of her achievements!", "recommendations/12/name": "Ryena Mirchanddani", "recommendations/12/subtitle": "Key Skills-Revenue Optimization, RFP Management, Negotiation,Strategy development and implementation, revenue enhancement, Budgeting & Forecasting", "recommendations/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ryena-mirchanddani-81242647/", "recommendations/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAnZ7w4BMsFAm7UhHMcQ9j2ApgPBgBkQfl8", "recommendations/13/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Kritika directly", "recommendations/13/date": "July 3, 2020", "recommendations/13/description": "Kritika is a very energetic and adaptable professional. She thrives in a challenging environment and seeks to go above and beyond expectations. She was particularly instrumental during a period of transition at the hotel. Once she understood the direction, she committed herself to the cause, delivering extraordinary results. I would be happy to entrust her higher responsibility should a suitable opportunity arise, and I am confident she will come through jubilant!", "recommendations/13/name": "Kritika Arora", "recommendations/13/subtitle": "Human Resources Specialist", "recommendations/13/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kritika-arora-3b9b4121/", "recommendations/13/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAASeIP0BuvXND7i3rMLt2VLVGHrsb_pGEdw", "recommendations/14/date": "September 15, 2019", "recommendations/14/description": "A level headed professional with deep insights into strategy and positioning of busy branded hotels in a competitive market. Very stable and focused on her goals.", "recommendations/14/name": "Aparna Ghatwal", "recommendations/14/subtitle": "Director Sales and Marketing at The Park Hotels", "recommendations/14/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/aparna-ghatwal-bb437916/", "recommendations/14/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAANB_ngBCvw6vTIrhXBrjV4_1FQ-fvlygsU", "recommendations/15/date": "September 15, 2019", "recommendations/15/description": "It is so good to see Balagi develop into a confident property leader from an HoD when I last worked with him. He always was focused and determined in his role as EHK of a large, remote hotel where he handled various people and vendor challenges with a smile. I again had the pleasure of experiencing his hospitality, this time as a guest when he headed the Rooms Division of a multi property complex. I am sure we will see him soon in the role of a successful GM.", "recommendations/15/name": "Balagi Singh", "recommendations/15/subtitle": "General Manager at Accor Hotels - BW Hotelier Awards Midscale General Manager of the year -2022-2023", "recommendations/15/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/balagi-singh-a99b6353/", "recommendations/15/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAtiNFUBRf7Mnq2_5CLEM6XGNJLA65stLU0", "recommendations/16/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Tarun on the same team", "recommendations/16/date": "September 15, 2019", "recommendations/16/description": "Tarun left an indelible mark during our first interaction in his role as Human Resources for a subsidiary of an MNC hotel brand. He has a deep understanding of operational aspects of the business and manages to leverage the relationship effectively to deliver as a valuable Human Resource ally. He continues to support me in various ways and I wish him success and glory in all he does.", "recommendations/16/name": "Tarun Dua", "recommendations/16/subtitle": "Business | Ex-Hotelier", "recommendations/16/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/tarun-dua-77b95b38/", "recommendations/16/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAf4z48B7gGOEUsB8IWhTvqbvysCST366ig", "recommendations/17/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Pariva on the same team", "recommendations/17/date": "September 15, 2019", "recommendations/17/description": "I have known Pariva for decades now and seen her grow through her professional journey into an effective, affable and dynamic leader in the domain of her specialisation. With sound grounding in luxury, she has delivered results in portfolios ranging from a property sales role to a source market and above property too. Her exposure to multiple market segments and multiple markets across the Indian subcontinent and beyond make her a knowledge bank so valuable to any Organisation she works for. I wish her the best in her quest.", "recommendations/17/name": "Pariva Rustagi", "recommendations/17/subtitle": "Strategy & Growth II Commercial, Sales & Enablement II Diversity & Inclusion II Asia Pacific at Hilton", "recommendations/17/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/parivarustagi/", "recommendations/17/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAE_Zf4BtlCtUnQRAmh5G65SURBrJE-oX0Y", "recommendations/18/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Ruban but on different teams", "recommendations/18/date": "July 23, 2019", "recommendations/18/description": "Well, am I not privileged to call this young and dynamic professional a friend and colleague? Ruban has this unique charm and manages to inspire all those around him. A great sense of humour adds to his affable personality. A go getter for professional results, Ruban will go a long way in this industry.", "recommendations/18/name": "Ruban Das", "recommendations/18/subtitle": "Love All Serve All", "recommendations/18/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ruban-das-b8b7994/", "recommendations/18/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADT8FsBTOb8qqP9ScXssJWA8KQlcmN6hMU", "recommendations/19/context": "Aditya Shamsher was Prakhar's client", "recommendations/19/date": "July 23, 2019", "recommendations/19/description": "I have had the pleasure of working with Prakhar as a client and partner over several years now. What I appreciate most about him is his professional approach and consistent follow up. He works towards a win-win solution for his partners and has his pulse to the ground. Prakhar’s orientation to Hospitality is admirable and it’s always a pleasure to deal with him.", "recommendations/19/name": "Prakhar Bhardwaj", "recommendations/19/subtitle": "Media Sales | Marketing Strategy | TV | Digital | Print | Events | Business Development", "recommendations/19/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bprakhar/", "recommendations/19/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQImWkBplXkgMo3p4xl8rt2GViGdP3rBaw", "recommendations/20/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Rahul on the same team", "recommendations/20/date": "February 14, 2019", "recommendations/20/description": "Rahul proved to be an outstanding Sales support for me during his stint as the Head of Sales for the Northern Region in Starwood. During the time, I was heading Sales for the 427 rooms Westin Hyderabad, thus far the largest inventory Hotel in the Starwood portfolio. He was most understanding of the challenges, empathetic and supportive. What I also learnt further from my interactions with his team and my knowing him better over the years, is that he is a strong leader. He stands up for what is right and backs his team. He is a humble man who takes feedback constructively, and values relationships. He is one with a strong character and demonstrates loyalty and perseverance.", "recommendations/20/name": "Rahul Sharma", "recommendations/20/subtitle": "General Manager @ Marriott | Hotel Profitability & Guest Experience", "recommendations/20/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/rahul-sharma-2b53612a/", "recommendations/20/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAYacmkBkbYv4y4db5X2u5uztk_CBDmPY_w", "recommendations/21/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Amit directly", "recommendations/21/date": "January 10, 2018", "recommendations/21/description": "It is a pleasure to see Amit successful in his career and life. But nor surprising, given the fact that I literally 'acquired' him after his interview with me, snatching him away from another lucrative offer he had at the time. Amit was a go getter from the moment he joined my team at The Westin Hyderabad Mindspace which was struggling after a slow launch and positioning and market share challenges. Amit brought in a breath of fresh air along with his easy demeanor and team spirit. He was quick to start contributing to the team and helped the Hotel establish it's presence and subsequently, market leadership in a very dynamic and competitive market. He is excellent with processes and relationships at the same time and has very strong reasoning ability. He is an ideal hire for a position involving leadership and strategic orientation.", "recommendations/21/name": "Amit Prakash, EMCC-P, ACC, CBC", "recommendations/21/subtitle": "I help Leaders and Entrepreneurs become a Powerhouse and Achieve 2X Performance and sales in 6 months by Coaching them and Consulting their problems with a money back guarantee | High-Performance Leadership Coach", "recommendations/21/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/amit-prakash-motivus/", "recommendations/21/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWDmmcBXXZH79w0pdZUXaINvq4pz_llMV4", "recommendations/22/context": "Pawandeep was Aditya Shamsher's client", "recommendations/22/date": "April 15, 2017", "recommendations/22/description": "Pawan, as we fondly call him, has been a client and friend for years, almost since the beginning of my career when I managed the US Embassy account for Oberoi Hotels. Pawan at the time was in the travel section and subsequently grew to head the section along with additional responsibilities. Detail oriented with a deep understanding of his business, Pawan was the backbone for us in delivery of expectations, particularly during high profile visits. He worked with all vendors in a very amicable manner, extracting the best for his Organisation and the Vendor's, creating a win-win situation. On the personal front, he is a passionate body builder and a doting family man.", "recommendations/22/name": "Pawandeep Saggu", "recommendations/22/subtitle": "Strategic Advisor", "recommendations/22/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/pawandeep-saggu-27172026/", "recommendations/22/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAVyF3UBNHVdZ8hGYXOze0rIvCoZN700f-c", "recommendations/23/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Bhavna directly", "recommendations/23/date": "January 16, 2017", "recommendations/23/description": "I poached Bhavna from the airline business for my team @The Westin Hyderabad Mindspace. Even though new to the business and the city, Bhavna settled into the role very quickly. Always up for the challenge, she handled various obstacles including a language barrier and a very demanding business situation. Bhavna added a new life to the team with her sense of humor, her helpful and understanding attitude and amiable nature. Her background in various businesses helped her develop in analytics and business acumen. She is a team player and an effective resource on the team, focussing on contribution. ", "recommendations/23/name": "Bhavna T", "recommendations/23/subtitle": "Marketing Professional", "recommendations/23/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bhavnaduggal/", "recommendations/23/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJusGYBb8PAk15wP4ByMNOliik9qI14nCs", "recommendations/24/context": "Aditya Shamsher was senior to Karan but didn't manage Karan directly", "recommendations/24/date": "March 15, 2016", "recommendations/24/description": "I have worked with Karan on multiple assignments when he represented the biggest source market for me. Karan always stood out from the rest because of his deep understanding of the business, a 360 degrees view and a highly professional approach. Never to present an excuse, Karan has high standards of ethics and values which drive his approach towards his friends, clients and colleagues.", "recommendations/24/name": "Karan Kachru", "recommendations/24/subtitle": "Hospitality | Ex-Logistics | Entrepreneur", "recommendations/24/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/karan-kachru-56a0527/", "recommendations/24/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFAlaIBJ-WvbaCMP7g_JHNAcJNircGj2-o", "recommendations/25/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Sam directly", "recommendations/25/date": "December 28, 2015", "recommendations/25/description": "Soumik was assigned as a task force to my Hotel earlier this year, when we were in the midst of a multi dimensional transition. New Ownership and a conversion. Soumik stabilised a rocking boat in the F&B department, led from the front and delivered without hesit.ation. He also took initiatives in sharing best practices, laying down SOPs, training the team and also ensuring guest satisfaction. He went beyond his brief by further implementing the next level of brand standards, a big help at the time. He put in place a robust and dependable system that worked well until the arrival of a new F&B Leader. In short, Soumik demonstrated great leadership and inter-personal skills along with strong operations capability. A true asset to any GM.", "recommendations/25/name": "Sam Khan", "recommendations/25/subtitle": "Seasoned Operations Manager", "recommendations/25/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sam-khan-7a472240/", "recommendations/25/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAimR-wBuLxxGgLAWmXXAPgZ7SY7QD6CnU8", "recommendations/26/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Dhiraj on the same team", "recommendations/26/date": "December 28, 2015", "recommendations/26/description": "First, I would like to clarify that these words are written on my own initiative, and not solicited by Dhiraj. As I reflected on my professional journey over the past few years, I could not help but recognise the significant role that Dhiraj played. Destiny introduced him to me as I sought a new role at Shangri-La New Delhi due to a personal exigency requiring me to relocate to Delhi. I am fortunate to recall this interaction, and the ones we had thereafter as colleagues, as some of the most enriching with a HR Leader. Soft in demeanour, Dhiraj is a great motivator who bring out the best in people. Patient enough to handle some of the most challenging situations, A rare breed of HR professionals who understands the business and contributes to both sides of the balance sheet equally. Dhiraj truly demonstrates the maturity and stability of a seasoned HR Professional. I was deeply influenced by his style and in fact went on to pursue higher studies in HR, Dhiraj is a friend, colleague and mentor, even to his peers. I Wish him success and glory!", "recommendations/26/name": "Dhiraj Bhushan", "recommendations/26/subtitle": "Director of HR @ Shangri-La | MBA | Employee Benefits | CSR I Strategy I Rewards & Recognition I Mergers & Acquisitions I Employer Branding I Talent Acquisition & Development I Workforce Planning I Performance Management", "recommendations/26/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/dhiraj-bhushan-392b2a9/", "recommendations/26/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAHEu54B63Kd24CXF1fY6NM1IYqARpEVstY", "recommendations/27/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Durga directly", "recommendations/27/date": "December 11, 2015", "recommendations/27/description": "I selected Durga as a member of my Team in The Oberoi Grand, Kolkata in 2008. Though her stint was short, Durga had adjusted to the nuances of Hotel Sales & Marketing rather quickly. She was not just quick off the mark but also effective in cracking some difficult accounts for the Hotel. She played a significant role in the exceptional growth of the Hotel's revenue and profitability that year. I still remember her as a rather intelligent and witty member of the team.", "recommendations/27/name": "Durga Chakraborty", "recommendations/27/subtitle": "Branch Head - South India at DB Corp Ltd", "recommendations/27/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/durga-chakraborty/", "recommendations/27/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWbLTcBKJZcu6aDlTKa07GsBgoWAGENz2M", "recommendations/28/context": "Aditya Shamsher was senior to Divya but didn't manage Divya directly", "recommendations/28/date": "November 21, 2015", "recommendations/28/description": "I remember Divya as an extremely energetic, passionate and driven professional when I first worked with her in Hyatt Regency Delhi. Divya was extremely process oriented, yet managed to be the favourite of guests and clients.She never shied from additional work and in fact was always keen to learn more. Her greatest strength is her ability to get along with people and align the resources that help her deliver great results. I do hope Divya continues to achieve all that she truly deserves.", "recommendations/28/name": "Divya S.", "recommendations/28/subtitle": "20 years of Events & Sales Experience across Brands| Turnover & Change Champion| Strategic Planner- Space & Rate Management| Hands- on Trainer: Sales & IT systems| Pre-opening Events Specialist", "recommendations/28/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/divya-s-06798116/", "recommendations/28/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAANY2w8B_igf7-v0Wi6KPs1TXW_YnepNq-U", "recommendations/29/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Sandeep directly", "recommendations/29/date": "September 28, 2015", "recommendations/29/description": "It takes special skills to sail the Ship through a storm. Some sailors do it consistently. Sandeep helped not just sail the Hotel through troubled times (challenging would be an understatement) but also helped keep it afloat. A truly gifted professional, one that every leader would consider a blessing to have on the team. Sandeep kept the team motivated, alert and happy, with very meagre resources at his disposal. He would wear various hats depending on what the need of the hour was (e.g. Reservations Manager/ Front Office associate/ Bell boy/ purchase associate/ engineering associate etc.). His ability to handle complex IR issues in a IR hotbed was truly commendable. His peers and colleagues at Radisson Blu fondly remember him as a focussed, result oriented yet compassionate colleague. Sandeep does exceptionally well in trying circumstances.", "recommendations/29/name": "Sandeep Pathania", "recommendations/29/subtitle": "Director Of Human Resources at Azizi Developments Strategic HR Leader | Driving Talent Transformation, Expansion & Performance Optimization Across Global Teams", "recommendations/29/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandeep-pathania/", "recommendations/29/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAcBLyMBjJf55NDXfJOnsAMWqOpCMIOA4M0", "recommendations/30/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Abhishek directly", "recommendations/30/date": "February 27, 2015", "recommendations/30/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Chef Abhishek at Radisson Blu Haridwar. Chef, like the rest of the F&B team was suddenly presented with a renewed challenge of enhancing guest experience, quality and hygiene. A very hard working and passionate professional, Chef stood up to the occasion and truly demonstrated his skills, which have been honed on International waters (literally). A sharp surge in GSI was greatly attributed to the wonderful work done by Chef, both as a creator and Leader. Among the challenges thrown at him were to lead the Production and Service teams, which also was handled most admirably. Chef connects with his work emotionally, like an artist and likes to succeed. I look forward to working with Chef Abhishek again and together as a Team, win further accolades for the Hotel.", "recommendations/30/name": "Abhishek Kukreti", "recommendations/30/subtitle": "General Manager", "recommendations/30/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/abhishek-kukreti-66ba5275/", "recommendations/30/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA_-rjMBi9RnedPdqSy5oRXynaEp5u_8Flc", "recommendations/31/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Saurabh directly", "recommendations/31/date": "November 12, 2014", "recommendations/31/description": "I write this professional recommendation for Saurabh after observing him for almost a decade, in different roles, but with a single direction. Saurabh first impressed me a Sales Coordinator, with his understanding of the business, his follow ups and sales support. Over the years, he worked on my team, either directly or indirectly, and each time he only reposed my faith in his professional approach and sharp business acumen. As a Leader, Saurabh strives to empower his team through training and pretty much leads by example. Never shy to roll up his sleeves and get his hands dirty, Saurabh inspires people around him to 'think'. This makes him a strategist and a planner. Saurabh has a natural flair for networking, adapts quickly and develops knowledge about the environment using relationships as a tool. I see a strong business leader in Saurabh, who has already shouldered challenging responsibilities  - personally and professionally at a fairly young age...", "recommendations/31/name": "Saurabh Khurana", "recommendations/31/subtitle": "Luxury Hospitality Business Leader | Growth Catalyst| 21+ Yrs in Luxury Hospitality | Driving Revenue, Guest Experience & Brand Growth | The Lodhi | Ex-Oberoi, Leela, Starwood”", "recommendations/31/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/saurabh-khurana-b734284/", "recommendations/31/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADGTocBeWzO9GU0yFaJiQ1oGzZHXd7dUmw", "recommendations/32/context": "Colonel Jasbir Singh was Aditya Shamsher's client", "recommendations/32/date": "September 17, 2014", "recommendations/32/description": "I had the pleasure of making Col Cheema's acquaintance while pitching The Oberoi Grand Kolkata for the stay of officials and dignitaries of OFB in Kolkata. Colonel impressed me most with his warm nature and a stoic, professional approach, when in uniform. In civvies, he is a delightful friend with a great sense of humor and dedication. Together, we worked on our Golf, challenging each other at times. Colonel Cheema is a true Army man, with deep rooted values and a strong patriotic streak. His assignment at OFB also gave him a detailed exposure to the Corporate world.", "recommendations/32/name": "Colonel Jasbir Singh Cheema", "recommendations/32/subtitle": "Expertise - Operations, Admin, Security, Managing Organization at Different Geographies.", "recommendations/32/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/colonel-jasbir-singh-cheema-b0622215/", "recommendations/32/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMO3bYByMW-CQ6n0oVjxyWPF1ZCep3YlPU", "recommendations/33/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Pooja directly", "recommendations/33/date": "September 1, 2013", "recommendations/33/description": "Pooja is a creative and enthusiastic Marketing professional.\n\nPooja showed high level of dedication and perseverance during her assignment at The Westin Mumbai Garden City through difficult times. She assumed additional resposibilities willingly and contributed significantly towards the repositioning the Hotel and improving the visibility through Social Media and Ground Activation.\n\nPooja is a result oriented, hard working professional who does not hesitate to chart into unfamiliar territory. Her strengths are relationships and her ability to get the best out of people, her team, vendors, Media and Internal customers. She is driven by Quality, Challenges and a hunger to learn and achieve!\n\nA great asset to an Organisation looking for solutions oriented, hard working, focussed creative and committed individuals.", "recommendations/33/name": "Pooja Vaswaney", "recommendations/33/subtitle": "Employee Experience Partner at Oxford International Education Services", "recommendations/33/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/pooja-vaswaney-b4322951/", "recommendations/33/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAArjzSMB_-KtMJs5lbeNH21P5Zj0MOiydrg", "recommendations/34/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Barun directly", "recommendations/34/date": "July 5, 2013", "recommendations/34/description": "Barun worked with me in two assignments, once directly reporting to me, and then as part of the biggest source market for my Hotel. Barun is a sincere, hard working, persevering person who likes to be known for his good work. He strives to exceed the expectations of the Organisation and deliver exceptional results for his team. Assertive, competent and a team player, is how I see Barun. Over the years I have known him, he has evolved as a strategist with high business acumen, driven by strong relationships with his clients. He commands respect and admiration of his customers and colleagues.", "recommendations/34/name": "Barun G.", "recommendations/34/subtitle": "Chief Operating Officer - Indeva Hotels & Resorts/ Global 100 Most Influential People in Event Industry 2022/2024/ 2025 & 50 Most Influential People in the Events Industry in Asia 2024/ 2025 by Eventex", "recommendations/34/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/barungupta/", "recommendations/34/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAGbT6cBdMH5Ib9bLS6Gl0gXNA2TdXwotzM", "recommendations/35/context": "Aditya Shamsher was senior to Siddharth but didn't manage Siddharth directly", "recommendations/35/date": "May 31, 2013", "recommendations/35/description": "I've known Siddharth over the years, both as a professional and as a friend. We worked in the same department when he was Reservations Manager and I was Associate Director of Sales at Hyatt Regency Delhi. Siddharth's single minded focus on his work and career impressed me most. He planned things meticulously and then focussed on achieving his goals. Be it his desire to head the department, pursue further education or invest in his career, often taking calculated risks. I have seen him evolve as an effective leader, both in business and people. A humble personality complemented by throrough professionalism, Siddharth has shown perseverence and resolve in testing times. He has also exhibited maturity in handling tricky situations impacting long term and short term business goals of the unit. Siddharth is a quick learner and is ready for greater challenges in a branded luxury hotel.", "recommendations/35/name": "Siddharth Varma", "recommendations/35/subtitle": "Luxury Hotelier | VP-Ops. | Ex- Shangri-La, Taj, Oberoi, Hyatt |", "recommendations/35/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sidvarma/", "recommendations/35/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAD-hGoBOQCYL-G408sl8tcLmlXp4OQkTPM", "recommendations/36/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Megha but on different teams", "recommendations/36/date": "April 17, 2013", "recommendations/36/description": "Megha is a self motivated, hard working and committed individual. She can juggle multiple tasks at the same time. Megha is ambitious and a good leader. She has good business acumen and excellent relationships in the market. It was a pleasure to work with her,", "recommendations/36/name": "Megha Ajgaonkar", "recommendations/36/subtitle": "Luxury Hospitality Sales | VP - Sales, The Leela | Driving Growth, Teams & Customer-Centric Culture | Award-Winning Hotelier", "recommendations/36/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/megha-ajgaonkar-2720a77/", "recommendations/36/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFCSrYBVjzT-kmeLmbNiOr1vkT_mzgrLB0", "recommendations/37/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Soumik directly", "recommendations/37/date": "February 17, 2013", "recommendations/37/description": "Soumik, aka 'Shivaji'. Named so for his swift moves, his single minded focus, strategic vision and a never say die attitude. Be it the toughest account, or a daunting task, Soumik plunged in with a fierce desire to win. I was privileged to him on my team during a very challenging period for the hotel. Initially entrusted with the task of building relationships and moving business very quickly, Soumik soon proved himself fit to handle bigger responsibilities. He was given another difficult task to take over the Banquet Sales department, calling upon his F&B, Sales and people management skills. Soon enough, Soumik had turned the tide there as well. A dreamer, Soumik also chases them well. He is a multi-tasker and is doing very well, both in his career and his passion - music.", "recommendations/37/name": "Soumik Ghosh", "recommendations/37/subtitle": "Strategic Marketing & Brand Leader | Growth-Driven Business Consultant | CXO Advisory | Head of Marketing I Times (BCCL) | Ex Zee | HT Media | D&B | Reliance | Vodafone | Oberoi Group Of Hotels | TajSats | Wipro", "recommendations/37/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/soumik-ghosh-ab302014/", "recommendations/37/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALZqCcBAx9z8-djTaFl9xUwSTBRYVmq-Pc", "recommendations/38/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Deepak but on different teams", "recommendations/38/date": "December 27, 2012", "recommendations/38/description": "Deepak was one of my first colleagues in the industry, and soon we became friends.We started our career on the same day in 1994 with the same brand, selling two different properties of the chain in Delhi. Deepak always inspired everyone around with his infectious energy and drive. Always cheerful, Deepak understood the business very well and chased it even better.He built strong relationships in the market, increasing the recall of our growing brand. He is a loyal, honest and highly productive resource with strong leadership skills.", "recommendations/38/name": "Deepak Dahiya", "recommendations/38/subtitle": "Director Of Business Development at Drehomes Real Estate", "recommendations/38/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/deepak-dahiya-9310257/", "recommendations/38/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAE_uPUB6KxAQ_4dzRNKzd8rGm2c38Rq-6M", "recommendations/39/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Sachin directly", "recommendations/39/date": "October 7, 2012", "recommendations/39/description": "I consider myself fortunate to have had the opportunity to lead a uniquely passionate team in The Westin Hyderabad Mindspace, and Sachin was among the senior members of this team, to begin with. I liken Sachin is a diligent worker with a huge potential, partly untapped. His attitude towards work, with a keenness to push himself and redefine boundaries sets his apart. A genuinely sincere human, Sachin focusses on his objectives without distraction. He has the ability to keep everyone around in good humor, even in the most tense situations.\nSachin developed as a leader under me and soon one could see the transformation from doing things well to motivating and inspiring others to excel.A hands on approach and customer focus helps him add value to his team mates, thereby earning their respect and admiration. He finds himself in the hot seat repeatedly, but manages to come out a winner. Part of our 'winning team' I would love to have Sachin on my team again.", "recommendations/39/name": "Sachin Didolkar", "recommendations/39/subtitle": "General Manager at Marriott International | Trekker | Mountaineer | Runner", "recommendations/39/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sachin-didolkar-74bb3210/", "recommendations/39/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJNiKsBBCDNYl4NdYMLcYbR77XHB3Kg7YE", "recommendations/40/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Amarinder on the same team", "recommendations/40/date": "July 25, 2012", "recommendations/40/description": "Amarinder and I worked closely as a crack team at The Westin Hyderabad Mindspace. I got to know him very well during this time and would like to compliment him on his professionalism, maturity and perseverence. Amarinder is very structured in his approach and creative in his thinking. There was hardly a challenge he did not think a solution for. Inquisitive, Amarinder's hunger to learn takes him places. Winning is his passion and strategy his weapon !! wish we can work together as a team again soon.", "recommendations/40/name": "Amarinder Sadana", "recommendations/40/subtitle": "Head of Commercial", "recommendations/40/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/amarindersadana/", "recommendations/40/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMn12ABGk2nZlhCMMr0UAvVajXlzkwzZi4", "recommendations/41/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Debanjan directly", "recommendations/41/date": "July 1, 2012", "recommendations/41/description": "First, a hearty congratulations on a well deserved promotion. I've said it often that I see a reflection of myself in DK. Clear vision, structured priorities, hard work, initiative, receptable to feedback, upright with strong values....the makings of a successful leader. It's never about reaching there, it's about staying there and holding fort. Debanjan made me proud yet again for being the youngest to lead the Sales function in a 427 rooms inventory hotel. I have never been disappointed by him and each time I raised the bar, DK managed to clear it without fumble. A professional with immense potential, DK has managed to earn the love, respect and admiration of his team, his peers and his superiors. The next time I put together a crack team, as always, DK will receive the first call!", "recommendations/41/name": "Debanjan Kundu (CHBA)", "recommendations/41/subtitle": "Sales Maverick I Success Strategist I SaaS Enthusiast I P&L Management I Revenue Leadership | Luxury Guest Experience Curator | Love to Network | Helping Hotel Brands Grow through Data-Driven Strategies", "recommendations/41/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/debanjan-kundu/", "recommendations/41/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALEbSYBRN5CVfE8lv1J60FVJqHDfVieDrQ", "recommendations/42/context": "Aditya Shamsher was Akshaya's client", "recommendations/42/date": "May 3, 2012", "recommendations/42/description": "Akshaya impressed me during her first meeting to present Zomato as a solution for our Food and Beverage marketing needs.\n\nShe approached us inspite of hurdles presented by layers within the organisation. Had done her homework well and made a crisp and effective presentation to generate interest and take the deal to closure. She not only worked with us to sell her product/ service, but also assisted us in identifying areas where we could improve delivery. She was committed to adding value to our business.\n\nSo effective was her commitment, that we engaged Zomato in my new assignment at Westin Mumbai as well.\n\nAkshaya is a brilliant professional who wins the trust of her clients with commitment and value creation. I wish her all the best for her future endeavours, and would in fact, be delighted to have her on my team in the future.", "recommendations/42/name": "Akshaya Nandakumar", "recommendations/42/subtitle": "Freelance Marketing Professional", "recommendations/42/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/cakshayan/", "recommendations/42/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAARd7g4BivYYfY1YYAqRxggVgTLVji0MxYI", "recommendations/43/context": "Aditya Shamsher was senior to Sachin but didn't manage Sachin directly", "recommendations/43/date": "July 16, 2011", "recommendations/43/description": "I have worked with Sachin long enough to see him promoted from F & B Manager to Asst Director and now Director F & B, which is all of 8 months! Sachin is a passionate and enterprising professional always hungry for more. He has exhibited his creative skills in setting up award winning restaurants and executing large scale, complex events successfully. He was part  of the pre-opening team, and hence has shown his strength in setting up processes and systems. He is a great team player who respects the strengths and knowledge of each member of the team. He is able to connect with and motive his team to deliver outstanding results. He will make an excellent General Manager soon.", "recommendations/43/name": "Sachin Mylavarapu", "recommendations/43/subtitle": "General Manager-JW Marriott Mumbai", "recommendations/43/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sachin-mylavarapu-66262810/", "recommendations/43/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAI6Y6oBPl1BbXuvB3n2pCkh_iRRyqCAEYA", "recommendations/44/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Maulina but on different teams", "recommendations/44/date": "May 1, 2011", "recommendations/44/description": "Energy, passion and delivery define Maulina as a professional sales and marketing resource. Very objective in her transactions and relationship driven, Maulina can turn situations to her advantage through her wit and determination. As an individual, she is mature and focussed. she has won the respect of her peers, seniors and her team! Well done Maulina!!", "recommendations/44/name": "Maulina Gupta", "recommendations/44/subtitle": "Vice President & Head of Asset", "recommendations/44/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/maulina-gupta-5680593/", "recommendations/44/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACKhOABtJA2HkNujK7CT228R6jJ_9L_oCQ", "recommendations/45/context": "Aditya Shamsher was Satyaki's client", "recommendations/45/date": "January 26, 2011", "recommendations/45/description": "Satyaki is very creative in his thought process. He flowcharts and understands the requirements very well. He also connects emotionally to an event/ task, thereby putting himself in the client's shoes. High on enthusiasm and self motivated, Satyaki leads his team to deliver beyond expectations. He visualises and proactively solves problems. Satyaki is also a great relationship builder and most clients cannot hire him just once!\nHis business acumen is led by a win-win approach which is productive for both - him and his clients. I have had the pleasure of having Satyaki handle some of the most challenging events and I cannot thank him enough. Looking forward to working with him again - soon !", "recommendations/45/name": "Satyaki Sengupta", "recommendations/45/subtitle": "Founder & CEO at Servmarc Communion Private Limited", "recommendations/45/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/satyaki-sengupta-3724226/", "recommendations/45/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAEhQYYBcH4EoS36qJwojTizGeovFj0WHNo", "recommendations/46/context": "Aditya Shamsher managed Manika directly", "recommendations/46/date": "January 26, 2011", "recommendations/46/description": "Manika is an ambitious, intelligent and level headed individual. High levels of determination and focus on objective are her key strengths. She has trained herself hard and worked on many aspects to improve and deliver, which is what has brought her such a long was in such a short time. She accepts challenges and takes initiatives. Manika is a quick learner and also enjoys life to the fullest. All the best Manika !", "recommendations/46/name": "Manika Das", "recommendations/46/subtitle": "Passionate Luxury Hotelier | Elevating Hospitality Excellence | Ex Oberoi, Marriott, Hyatt, Rotana, Dusitd2 & Millennium | Calcutta University ( B.SC), Diploma in Aviation & Hospitality Management AHA Delhi", "recommendations/46/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/manika-das-394a9613/", "recommendations/46/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALUa6ABDP0UdIcEsFcckcCqA5pTDuMMkyQ", "recommendations/47/context": "Aditya Shamsher worked with Neeta but they were at different companies", "recommendations/47/date": "November 25, 2010", "recommendations/47/description": "Neeta is the perfect ambassador of hospitality. She creates lasting impressions and builds long term relationships even in a brief interaction. An effective leader, Neeta carries her team along as a happy family. The smiles on the faces of her team members show that! Her sales and marketing experience helps her become a successful General Manager since a healthy GOP is the first objective of any business. From my experience as a guest at the property, Neeta focusses on the topline adequately to achieve that goal. All the best !", "recommendations/47/name": "Neeta Brid", "recommendations/47/subtitle": 