recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/soumodeep-bhattacharya-32634a21/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAR__U4BqnnXA9ZeIs16ENLxstKO5ah-5yY", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Mayank worked with Aditya Shamsher but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/8/date": "January 14, 2013", "recommendationsReceived/8/description": "A consumate professional and a committed value driver on all aspects of revenue and client relationships, Aditya is a man to watch out for. He will go far. And I wish him all the best!", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "Mayank Dhingra", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "Global Education Business Leader | Board Member | AI & EdTech", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mdhingra/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAA_tlMB4HebJ546PfjPhfr6mEOsYlJKHw0", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "Amarinder worked with Aditya Shamsher on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "July 10, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/9/description": "Aditya has a dynamic personality and is very professional in his work style. He is one of the great Sales and Marketing leader who believes in team work and bonds well with everyone. He strongly believes in Revenue Management and supports the function well with his experience. We together at Westin Hyderabad had achieved great results and laid strong foundation and base to the hotel. A great friend and a better human being. I wish him and his family best of luck for future endeavours..", "recommendationsReceived/9/name": "Amarinder Sadana", "recommendationsReceived/9/subtitle": "Head of Commercial", "recommendationsReceived/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/amarindersadana/", "recommendationsReceived/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMn12ABGk2nZlhCMMr0UAvVajXlzkwzZi4", "recommendationsReceived/10/context": "Francis worked with Aditya Shamsher on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/10/date": "July 8, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/10/description": "I worked with Aditya and know him personally for the last three years.I am extremely glad to testify Aditya as a go-getter and a through professional. His strategic approach was instrumental in Westin Hyderabad achieving  great heights in revenue as well as brand visibility. Soft in approach, pleasing in manners, this team player enjoys a great net work of colleagues and friends. Aditya will be a strong asset to any organization that he belongs to.", "recommendationsReceived/10/name": "Francis Ambatt", "recommendationsReceived/10/subtitle": "VP - Talent & Growth Strategy - Hotels Preopening & Start Up, HR Branding, Change Management, Mentoring, Training and Employee career cycle enhancement", "recommendationsReceived/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/francis-ambatt-6901033/", "recommendationsReceived/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACMlAwBd5mOpxpf4MeUJis2x5SjlOs6nzY", "recommendationsReceived/11/context": "Shoumo managed Aditya Shamsher directly", "recommendationsReceived/11/date": "February 25, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/11/description": "Aditya Malla's greatest qualities , particularly evident during his tenure with me at Oberoi Hotels in Calcutta are his determination and focus . In a challenging situation , when there is extreme pressure to perform Aditya Malla is an absolute asset to have . He is thorough and approaches situations with complete professionalism . His professional integrity is absolute and impeccable .Time and again he has demonstrated his ability to perform. In his capacity as Asst Sales Manager he achieved significant marketshare growth in key national accounts for Oberoi Hotels .", "recommendationsReceived/11/name": "Shoumo Mukherjee", "recommendationsReceived/11/subtitle": "Maldives expert", "recommendationsReceived/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/shoumo-mukherjee67722b/", "recommendationsReceived/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAZXjPoBdDA-earKSwUI7bQpJaQEznNLvok", "recommendationsReceived/12/context": "Anish was senior to Aditya Shamsher but didn't manage Aditya Shamsher directly", "recommendationsReceived/12/date": "February 23, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/12/description": "Aditya was an absolute delight to work with - a people person with a strong nose for business, he was an achiever in his role as Director Sales at The Oberoi, Grand. \nHis ideas, based on his deep knowledge of the hospitality business and insights into corporate travel behaviour, were invaluable to the entire team. I thoroughly enjoyed our interactions and always remember having learned from them. I wish him all the very best!", "recommendationsReceived/12/name": "Anish Srikrishna", "recommendationsReceived/12/subtitle": "Former CEO at TimesPro | Building the Next Chapter", "recommendationsReceived/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/anishsrikrishna/", "recommendationsReceived/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAcAEkBIiOF8szHQwd2xT8sWJDtWq2pAOM", "recommendationsReceived/13/context": "Vijay Ramamoorthy reported directly to Aditya Shamsher", "recommendationsReceived/13/date": "May 14, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/13/description": "Aditya is a fine hotelier from sales point of view. \n\nHis ability to enhance the imagination of the buyer is phenomenal and more often than not he is able to convince a client why that little premium (which he pays by chosing Oberoi) would help. He is brilliant in building around a niche concept may it be an innovative way of doing a conference or be it a simple meeting. \n\nA good teacher, Aditya has great presentation skills. Even in an impromptu situation, he can easily deliver slick presentations. I would always wish to see him as a head of an events/conventions team in a country-lead role since I think his forte would come into full play in a role like that.\n\nI enjoyed immense space and freedom as a second-in-command and that experience definitely added to my growth.", "recommendationsReceived/13/name": "Vijay Ramamoorthy Iyer", "recommendationsReceived/13/subtitle": "Reimagining Hospitality with AI | Oberoi Alumni (19+ yrs) | VOIZ | Ex-Four Seasons |", "recommendationsReceived/13/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/vijayramamoorthyiyer/", "recommendationsReceived/13/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAC01vYBOyS8w8bW2vgHl8I0YhtznMvnJIo", "recommendationsReceived/14/context": "Soumava worked with Aditya Shamsher but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/14/date": "May 10, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/14/description": "Aditya is a great human being and a wonderful individual.I have had the opportunity to work very closely with Aditya through KOLKATA SKAL CHAPTER from April 2009 onwards (we are a part of the office bearer committee) and always found him to be very systematic, energetic, a person with full of passion and drive in whatever he does. His positive, gentleman attitude and warm personality is what one will come across first. Aditya is a true winner and a person of principle and value. He makes any job look so easy, and that is his style of working I guess!!\nHe is an asset for any corporate organisation or even for any social body. His networking skills are excellent !\nIn the true spirit of SKAL, I wish Aditya - good health, prosperity and success !!", "recommendationsReceived/14/name": "Soumava Mukherjee", "recommendationsReceived/14/subtitle": "General Manager | Travel, Aviation & GDS | 25 Years | Leadership | Strategy, Revenue Growth & Partnerships | Ex-GMR Airport, InterGlobe(Travelport), Tata AIG, Airtel, Singapore Airlines, Taj & Jet Airways.", "recommendationsReceived/14/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/soumavamukherjee/", "recommendationsReceived/14/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAID0ekB6_bJqVzZ7WJkCA6LJFAaqb0v1Ak", "recommendationsReceived/15/context": "Ashwinder worked with Aditya Shamsher but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/15/date": "May 10, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/15/description": "I have known Aditya over a good period of time now and i can confidently say that he is an excellent organiser, great on integrity, has indepth knowledge of his work and a keen planner. On a personal note a great friend who who one can rely on.\nAshwinder", "recommendationsReceived/15/name": "Ashwinder Singh", "recommendationsReceived/15/subtitle": "Operating Officer - General Purchase at Honda Motorcycle & Scooter India Pvt Ltd", "recommendationsReceived/15/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ashwinder-singh-4714367/", "recommendationsReceived/15/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFPPhUB3Iuzpv5SSE_CRglxb-BIVO5BHvM", "recommendationsReceived/16/context": "Aditya Shamsher was senior to Priya but didn't manage Priya directly", "recommendationsReceived/16/date": "July 28, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/16/description": "Aditya is a highly motivated professional  .I have enjoyed working with him in two different organizations Oberoi and Hyatt. His key skills are networking, dedication to his work, good varied knowledge of the hotel industry at all levels. He has accomplished a much well deserved success over the years. I wish him all the very best for present and future.", "recommendationsReceived/16/name": "Priya Sahni", "recommendationsReceived/16/subtitle": "Experienced & Dynamic Marketer with a strong service industry background.", "recommendationsReceived/16/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/priya22/", "recommendationsReceived/16/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFZk1wBPuNa_D7GH48e0LjOa5l0rs2BniA", "recommendationsReceived/17/context": "Aditya Shamsher was senior to Shamein but didn't manage Shamein directly", "recommendationsReceived/17/date": "July 23, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/17/description": "I think it's safe to say that Aditya was the single-most dedicated individual at TKO at the time. A complete task master, sharp as a hawk, who took on more than his share of responsibility in everything. With an impressive educational background, even this early on in his career, he had exceptional discipline and outstanding work ethics. Being a highly motivated and ambitious person, Aditya has accomplished much well-deserved success over the years and has extreme potential to reach further heights in his professional life. I wish him all the very best.", "recommendationsReceived/17/name": "Shamein Qadri", "recommendationsReceived/17/subtitle": "Realtor at Serhant", "recommendationsReceived/17/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/shameinqadri/", "recommendationsReceived/17/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABX7AkBfy4YdrP5XLKXb1dfbUeSqLGReY0", "recommendationsReceived/18/context": "Deepak worked with Aditya Shamsher but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/18/date": "July 23, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/18/description": "Thorough bred Sales & Marketing Professional, Completely switched on & with a drive to continuosly evolve & deliver excellence, hands on approach. Aditya is fantastic !!! Good luck.", "recommendationsReceived/18/name": "Deepak Dahiya", "recommendationsReceived/18/subtitle": "Director of Sales & Marketing at Gold Swiss-Belhotel Dubai", "recommendationsReceived/18/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/deepak-dahiya-6693704/", "recommendationsReceived/18/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADD3rEBjH9WiUPyF06weo_-YMveFRUc9cQ", "recommendationsReceived/19/context": "Jalaja worked with Aditya Shamsher on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/19/date": "July 22, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/19/description": "Aditya is a highly motivated person full of energy and enthusiasm. I thouroughly enjoyed working with him during my tenure at the Oberoi hotels. He is very strong with his networking and collaboration skills. Very Client focussed and committed, he played a key role in moving some very important clients to the Oberoi Hotels while we worked together. He will always be an asset to any organisation that he works for and I wish him all the very best, at all times.", "recommendationsReceived/19/name": "Jalaja Pillai", "recommendationsReceived/19/subtitle": "- Leadership/Executive/Team Coaching - Learning, Leadership and Organizational Development - DEI and Culture, Women’s Leadership Development - Emotional Wellness, Mental Health, Counselling and Psychotherapy", "recommendationsReceived/19/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jalaja/", "recommendationsReceived/19/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACQUXcB8pY2WYFasgcqNPg5yNsVtu_T7Lk", "recommendationsReceived/20/context": "Paul was senior to Aditya Shamsher but didn't manage Aditya Shamsher directly", "recommendationsReceived/20/date": "July 22, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/20/description": "Aditya is a dilligent, hard working individual with a good intellect and a passion to succeed. His achievements in his current role have been very impressive. He is able to combine sound man management skills with strategic goal setting and delivery. I have no hesitation in recommending him.", "recommendationsReceived/20/name": "Paul Simmons", "recommendationsReceived/20/subtitle": "✈️ Aviation & Travel Executive | Non-Executive Director | Strategic Advisor", "recommendationsReceived/20/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/paul-simmons-9008463/", "recommendationsReceived/20/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACogZABAozjdPX8zzrA6JtF8bUaO4OatTQ", "recommendationsReceived/21/context": "Manish  managed Aditya Shamsher directly", "recommendationsReceived/21/date": "July 22, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/21/description": "I have had the pleasure of working with Aditya even before Hyatt, at the Krishna Oberoi Hyderabad.It was wonderful working with him. I have always found his dedication, eye for detail and no nonsense attitude, very refreshing indeed.", "recommendationsReceived/21/name": "Manish  K.", "recommendationsReceived/21/subtitle": "Founder SOUTH ASIAN ASSOCIATION FOR GASTRONOMY-FOOD FOR THOUGHT FEST, India’s Globally Recognised International Event | Art Collector | HAUTE Services- Boutique Consultancy for Luxury & Lifestyle", "recommendationsReceived/21/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/manish-kumar-baheti/", "recommendationsReceived/21/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADkYXwBzH6hVi-82DWcH7ZfaCqr2JPKv7k", "recommendationsReceived/22/context": "Prabhjot Singh worked with Aditya Shamsher on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/22/date": "July 14, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/22/description": "Aditya Shamsher is what his name suggests, a Tiger!\n\nExtremely well connected (networked), society savvy and a pro at finding business he is a fantastic sales & marketing leader.  \n\nWhat sets him apart though, is his love for operations and keen sense of processes.  He should be leading his own team at a hotel and I suspect he will, very very soon!", "recommendationsReceived/22/name": "Prabhjot Singh Bedi", "recommendationsReceived/22/subtitle": "Founder, Eclat Hospitality | Editor, hospemag.me", "recommendationsReceived/22/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/prabhjotbedi/", "recommendationsReceived/22/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACJAAsBGVsDMPHlwE16kxJXUG-GruxXXl8", "recommendationsReceived/23/context": "Joy worked with Aditya Shamsher on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/23/date": "June 23, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/23/description": "I worked with Aditya the first time as his client. Later I worked with him as a colleague. We have seen each other in different roles in different geographies. However, the friendship we developed from our first meeting remains unchanged in the last fifteen years of our association. We can start from where we left off last time without feeling the time lapse affecting our communication!\nIn a literal sense I learnt the basics of hotel sales & marketing from Aditya. The first thing that comes to my mind when I think of Aditya as a professional is his methodical approach to work. He is clinically accurate in his planning and delivery.\nTo top that, the man surely is suave and has style. \nAditya's world of ethics is very black and white... there are no shades of grey. You surely will have a problem if you are a fence sitter with him.\nIn the last few years, he has earned my additional admiration by displaying his qualities of consistency and stability.\nKeep going my friend!", "recommendationsReceived/23/name": "Joy Ghosh", "recommendationsReceived/23/subtitle": "Head of Commercial, Hospitality - Indian Subcontinent, Middle East, Africa and Turkey at Amadeus", "recommendationsReceived/23/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ghoshjoy/", "recommendationsReceived/23/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACNL38BFIVs6axICFDQPQPdPuEYw9cVeA8", "recommendationsReceived/24/context": "Sandeep worked with Aditya Shamsher but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/24/date": "May 14, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/24/description": "A very dynamic & professional Sales Director at Oberoi ! It was indeed a pleasure being associated with him and our inter-action was excellant. He was always supportive of our requirements and we worked well together.\n\nA great fan of travelling & enjoying life !", "recommendationsReceived/24/name": "Sandeep Mukherjee", "recommendationsReceived/24/subtitle": "Expertise in Airlines/Ground Operations/GHSP & Airport Services. Available for consulting/contractual services to enhance Safety Compliances, DGCA Regulatory Compliances & ISAGO standards for GHSP & Regulatory Manuals", "recommendationsReceived/24/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sandeepmindia/", "recommendationsReceived/24/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKmtikByfDaCXsVdYLDPOn_pC5oEtZxlzk", "recommendationsReceived/25/context": "Shankar worked with Aditya Shamsher but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/25/date": "March 3, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/25/description": "Aditya can be summed up in a simple series of words - \"Dedicated\", \"High Energy\", \"Committed\" and \"Caring\". I greatly appreciated working with him at the Oberoi Hotels and can say that he infused me (as a relative newcomer and an internal customer of his) with his own unique \"infectious\" sense of humour coupled with great service, in some extremely trying circumstances (read: Sold Out Dates -The Hotel Sales Executive's Nightmare)!", "recommendationsReceived/25/name": "Shankar Balan", "recommendationsReceived/25/subtitle": "Chief Growth Officer - International Business & Airline Services at Pinelabs Pvt Ltd - Issuing Business", "recommendationsReceived/25/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/shankarbalan/", "recommendationsReceived/25/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABVdBMBvr1G0cmU5RPWTIJXXmzOo2ocGA0", "skills/0/title": "Food & Beverage", "skills/1/title": "Marketing", "skills/2/title": "Employee Training", "skills/3/title": "Repositioning", "skills/4/title": "Pre-opening", "skills/5/title": "Hotels", "skills/6/title": "Yield Management", "skills/7/title": "Restaurants", "skills/8/title": "Leisure", "skills/9/title": "Marketing Strategy", "skills/10/title": "Account Management", "skills/11/title": "Leadership", "skills/12/title": "Revenue Analysis", "skills/13/title": "Hospitality Industry", "skills/14/title": "Hotel Management", "skills/15/title": "Hospitality Management", "skills/16/title": "Training", "skills/17/title": "Sales", "skills/18/title": "Resorts", "skills/19/title": "Hospitality", "totalExperienceYears": "31.9", "totalRecommendationsGiven": "61", "totalRecommendationsReceived": "26", "urn": "ACoAAAEZjMABVGrR7Ur1VKTw3hu8JyhyOLJOLNc", "volunteerAndAwards/0/description": "IMT CDL Alumni Association is an active, elite Alumni Association of the esteemed and top ranked IMT Ghaziabad - Centre of Distance Learning", "volunteerAndAwards/0/duration/months": "0", "volunteerAndAwards/0/duration/years": "0", "volunteerAndAwards/0/end_date/month": "0", "volunteerAndAwards/0/end_date/year": "0", "volunteerAndAwards/0/industry": "Social_services", "volunteerAndAwards/0/is_current_position": "true", "volunteerAndAwards/0/organization": "IMT CDL Ghaziabad", "volunteerAndAwards/0/role": "Executive Committee Membe