t - MGallery Collection", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/last_name": "Viou", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/premium": "false", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/public_identifier": "pierre-yves-viou-95b811a", "peopleAlsoViewed/25/url": "https://linkedin.com/in/ACoAAAHmXRcB0KHDUhX1HCMfQgYXcZlEZp3K6Uw", "profilePic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQEgNOd9PGIO3A/profile-displayphoto-crop_800_800/B56ZoaHNHLJoAI-/0/1761374688740?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=Q2Cmgsre00TQVCEDet9LVSAiK9F2uZ9uc5i5Yz49W2Y", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQEgNOd9PGIO3A/profile-displayphoto-crop_800_800/B56ZoaHNHLJoAI-/0/1761374688740?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=Q2Cmgsre00TQVCEDet9LVSAiK9F2uZ9uc5i5Yz49W2Y", "publicIdentifier": "jon-warmington-9ab53211", "recommendations/0/date": "April 14, 2023", "recommendations/0/description": "Even though only working for us for a short period of time Due to Covid restrictions and lockdowns. Gabriel showed his true passion for with hospitality, no challenge to big or too small always willing to help. Always willing to learn never afraid to get stuck in. Definitely always willing to learn open to advice and follows the instructions extremely well.  Gabriel has the right attitude to succeed, and I would happily employed him again in the future. In a short period of time, he showed his true worth and was able to impact the team, not only with discipline, but also a with a smile and he always lead from the front and setting the right example. ", "recommendations/0/name": "Gabriel Goh King Howe CHT", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Learning & Development Manager", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabriel-goh-king-howe-cht-9a133513b/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACIK7kkBtrCf04ORSjBUvrjwPdkQ-lf7cHY", "recommendations/1/date": "February 11, 2023", "recommendations/1/description": "More than happy to recommend Khun Zarifa, previously worked with me at the Avani Atrium, where she began her time with us as Quality manager, Zarifa excelled in her work, through her dedication to exceed customer expectations.  A very strong team leader and would have definitely been considered for high management roles. I would re employ Zarifa providing I could find her the suitable role that would challenged her ability, She has more to offer and I hope to work with her again in the future.  Tenacious in maintaining the balance between driving  and supporting her teams whilst knowledgeable at the same time.  Very well liked by all and highly recognized by her regular and loyal customers.  Never say no attitude and striving to succeed always.\n\n", "recommendations/1/name": "Zarifa Mahamud", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Rooms Division Manager at Anantara Hotels, Resorts and Spas", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/zarifa-mahamud-b9707696/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABRMhiMB3Z-Ms7h87tPoH6Zjj4u11manIY4", "recommendations/2/date": "February 5, 2022", "recommendations/2/description": "Burt Michael, was one of our talented chef de parties when we opened Hilton Kota Kinabalu, solid performer, able to work within a team and alone. At times leading the team in our stunning poolside a la carte restaurant and fully engaged when assisting the banqueting team during large events. Strong eye for details, able to create dishes through sustainable sources, not limited to only local produce. Strong ability with varying cuts of meat. Positive young chef with talent to lead teams, we placed him as a culinary trainer during his time with us. You can count on Burt he won’t let you down.", "recommendations/2/name": "Burt Michael", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Sweat, Cuts, Burned, Blood, Tears, Satisfaction", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/burt-michael-09886a195/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAC3eGfQBQSkwoQ7MGuCO-d8uKaw_fI08-uc", "recommendations/3/context": "Jon was Daniel Masih's client", "recommendations/3/date": "December 4, 2017", "recommendations/3/description": "Daniel, has always been knowledgeable in providing win win solution for customers.  We have been dealing at three different properties, Hilton Kuching and Batang Ai longhouse and just recently Hilton Kota Kinabalu.\n\nAll with very different requirements , however Daniel was able to provide a tailor made solution that gave great results.  Pleasure to work with and polite and knowledgeable business to boot.", "recommendations/3/name": "Daniel Masih Jalal", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "General Manager at Sai Alupack Ltd", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/daniel-masih-jalal-7517792b/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAZXu-0BFXxXdSGuuLfHZyDBu2pY_uETw7w", "recommendations/4/context": "Jon managed Sinah directly", "recommendations/4/date": "December 4, 2017", "recommendations/4/description": "Sinah, worked constantly and consistently under various exec Housekeepers, during my time at Hilton kuching and Batang Ai longhouse.  Never was anything to much trouble she always had a strong focus on room cleanliness, whilst maintaining the discipline across the rooms and laundry section.  Was always well respected by her team and peers alike. Would definitely re employ sinah given the right opportunity.  Wish her every success\n", "recommendations/4/name": "Sinah Ebot", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Retired Hotelier", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sinahebot/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACKBvrcBsMUEKos-pmtLAG0YPqXpCCeWb9M", "recommendations/5/context": "Jon was senior to Emeka but didn't manage Emeka directly", "recommendations/5/date": "February 16, 2015", "recommendations/5/description": "Emeka,  Was a great team player able to understand eth change in business , was also keen to try new ideas, and willing to trust the operations team to deliver.  Whilst we changed how we did business at Transcorp and greatly improved our offering , in service and quality 